text.section:
The Board shall issue a restricted license only to an applicant who:
Was licensed to practice osteopathy in this State or in another state on June 30, 1980;
Is licensed to practice osteopathy in this State or in another state on the date that the application for a restricted license is submitted to the Board;
Submits an application to the Board on the form that the Board requires;
Pays to the Board the restricted license fee set by the Board; and
Meets any other requirement set by the Board.
